title: Where can I get support for my software or tech project?
text: TechSpark offers dedicated support for startups, developers, and businesses through our innovation lab, mentorship programs, and developer network. You can reach out via our support center or schedule a consultation with one of our tech advisors.

title: How much does it cost to build or use software through TechSpark?
text: Costs vary based on the scope of your project. We offer free consultations, startup-friendly packages, and enterprise-grade solutions. Some of our tools and learning programs are even free for students and early-stage innovators.

title: What kind of data do I need to get started with TechSpark tools?
text: To get started, you'll typically need basic information about your product idea, target users, and business goals. If you're joining a training or development program, you'll also be asked to submit relevant user data or project briefs to customize the experience.
